(define/contract (incremovable-subarray-count nums)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer?)

  (define (incremovable-helper n)
    (let ([dp (make-vector n 0)])
      (let loop ([i 0] [max-len 0])
        (when (< i n)
          (vector-set! dp i 1)
          (let loop-inner ([j 0])
            (when (< j i)
              (when (< (list-ref nums j) (list-ref nums i))
                (vector-set! dp i (max (vector-ref dp i) (+ 1 (vector-ref dp j)))))
              (loop-inner (+ j 1))))
          (loop (+ i 1) (max max-len (vector-ref dp i)))))
      dp))

  (define n (length nums))
  (define dp-lis (incremovable-helper n))
  (define dp-lds (incremovable-helper n))
  (define total 0)

  (for ([i (in-range n)])
    (set! total (+ total (- (+ (vector-ref dp-lis i) (vector-ref dp-lds i)) 1))))
  total)
